WEBVTT

00:00:11.100 --> 00:00:14.300
Narrator: IT SEEMS
EVERYWHERE WE LOOK,

00:00:14.300 --> 00:00:18.100
WE SEE WAR, DISEASE,

00:00:18.100 --> 00:00:20.760
TERROR, AND DEATH.

00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:27.260
WE SEE OPPRESSION,
DIVISION, AND VIOLENCE.

00:00:27.260 --> 00:00:37.330
WE SEE PAIN.

00:00:37.330 --> 00:00:39.300
YET THERE IS SOMETHING ELSE

00:00:39.300 --> 00:00:53.500
THAT IS ALSO HAPPENING
ALL AROUND US.

00:00:53.500 --> 00:00:58.860
95% OF US BELIEVE IN A POWER
GREATER THAN OURSELVES.

00:00:58.860 --> 00:01:02.100
WE BELIEVE THAT WE
CAN, THROUGH OUR FAITH,

00:01:02.100 --> 00:01:05.400
MAKE A DIFFERENCE IN THE WORLD.

00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:07.100
PEOPLE EVERYWHERE
WANT TO BELIEVE

00:01:07.100 --> 00:01:09.760
IN THE FUNDAMENTAL POWER OF GOOD

00:01:09.760 --> 00:01:14.860
AND THE POSSIBILITY FOR CHANGE.

00:01:14.860 --> 00:01:18.460
BEYOND OUR DIFFERENCES,
THERE IS A COMMON HOPE

00:01:18.460 --> 00:01:21.500
THAT BINDS US TOGETHER,
A PROFOUND SENSE

00:01:21.500 --> 00:01:26.260
THAT WHAT WE SHARE IS SACRED.

00:01:26.260 --> 00:01:43.130
WE ARE A PEOPLE OF FAITH.

00:01:43.130 --> 00:01:47.530
Young: MOST OF US THINK
WE'RE HUMAN BEINGS

00:01:47.530 --> 00:01:50.030
HAVING A SPIRITUAL EXPERIENCE,

00:01:50.030 --> 00:01:52.330
WHEN ACTUALLY IT'S
PROBABLY MORE ACCURATE

00:01:52.330 --> 00:01:59.030
THAT WE'RE SPIRITUAL BEINGS
HAVING A HUMAN EXPERIENCE.

00:01:59.030 --> 00:02:04.700
Chopra: SPIRITUALITY COMES
FROM THE DEPTH OF THE HEART

00:02:04.700 --> 00:02:08.100
TO RELATE TO GOD, THE CREATOR,

00:02:08.100 --> 00:02:15.100
AND EVERYONE DO
IT IN HIS OWN WAY.

00:02:15.100 --> 00:02:17.360
THAT'S HOW I DEFINE
SPIRITUAL EXPERIENCE,

00:02:17.360 --> 00:02:19.730
TO ENTER A DOMAIN OF AWARENESS

00:02:19.730 --> 00:02:30.530
WHERE YOU RECOGNIZE
YOUR UNIVERSALITY.

00:02:30.530 --> 00:02:34.000
Tutu: THE HUMAN BEING IS CREATED

00:02:34.000 --> 00:02:37.300
IN THE IMAGE OF
THE DIVINE BEING,

00:02:37.300 --> 00:02:41.530
WHICH MAKES A HUMAN
BEING, EVERY HUMAN BEING,

00:02:41.530 --> 00:02:46.500
NOT JUST IMPORTANT, BUT
SOMEONE OF INFINITE WORTH.

00:02:46.500 --> 00:02:48.800
WHEN WE SEE GOD IN ALL,

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:52.700
THEN WE ARE ONLY THEN
BEGINNING TO SEE GOD.

00:02:52.700 --> 00:02:56.660
Armstrong: RELIGION IS THE QUEST

00:02:56.660 --> 00:02:59.260
FOR A TRANSCENDENT
VISION THAT ENABLES US

00:02:59.260 --> 00:03:01.160
TO MAKE SENSE OF OUR WORLD

00:03:01.160 --> 00:03:05.000
AND OUR RELATIONSHIP
TO OTHER PEOPLE,

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:07.930
A QUEST FOR MEANING,

00:03:07.930 --> 00:03:20.800
AND A DESIRE TO
BECOME FULLY HUMAN.

00:03:20.800 --> 00:03:26.660
Lord Carey: RELIGION IS A
POWERFUL FORCE FOR GOOD--

00:03:26.660 --> 00:03:29.100
THE EMPHASIS UPON THE FAMILY,

00:03:29.100 --> 00:03:30.530
COMMITMENT TO MARRIAGE,

00:03:30.530 --> 00:03:33.230
A COMMITMENT OF ETHICAL
FRAMEWORK FOR LIFE,

00:03:33.230 --> 00:03:34.530
A COMMITMENT TO CHILDREN,

00:03:34.530 --> 00:03:40.660
A COMMITMENT TO SOCIAL ORDER,
TO PEACE AND STABILITY.

00:03:40.660 --> 00:03:44.130
THE VALUES OF JUSTICE,
THE VALUES OF CHARITY,

00:03:44.130 --> 00:03:47.800
THE VALUES OF
PROTECTION OF THE POOR,

00:03:47.800 --> 00:03:52.960
THE VALUES OF...OF CREATING
SOCIAL SAFETY NETS.

00:03:52.960 --> 00:03:54.500
THESE ARE RELIGIOUS VALUES.

00:03:54.500 --> 00:03:58.400
Tutu: HUMAN BEINGS
ARE MORAL BEINGS,

00:03:58.400 --> 00:04:02.600
AND RELIGION TRIES TO
ENCOURAGE ITS ADHERENCE

00:04:02.600 --> 00:04:09.830
TO SEEK TO DO THE GOOD AND
TO AVOID THE BAD, THE EVIL.

00:04:09.830 --> 00:04:16.260
RELIGION IS THE PRIMARY
FUNDAMENTAL RELATIONSHIP

00:04:16.260 --> 00:04:21.230
BETWEEN A CREATURE
AND ITS CREATOR.

00:04:21.230 --> 00:04:35.100
[MEN CHANTING]

00:04:35.100 --> 00:04:36.500
Rosen: IF GOD RELATES TO US

00:04:36.500 --> 00:04:38.800
AND HAS CREATED US
IN ALL OUR DIVERSITY,

00:04:38.800 --> 00:04:41.060
THEN OBVIOUSLY THERE
ARE UNLIMITED WAYS

00:04:41.060 --> 00:04:42.660
OF RELATING TO GOD.

00:04:42.660 --> 00:04:45.600
YOU CAN NEVER UNDERSTAND
THE TOTALITY OF THE DIVINE

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:46.960
BECAUSE WE'RE NOT GOD.

00:04:46.960 --> 00:04:50.500
AND THEREFORE ANY RELIGION
IS ONLY A PARTIAL GLIMPSE

00:04:50.500 --> 00:04:52.300
INTO THAT ETERNAL TRUTH,

00:04:52.300 --> 00:05:06.560
AND NONE OF US CAN HAVE MORE
THAN A PARTIAL GLIMPSE.

00:05:06.560 --> 00:05:09.100
Jones: SPIRITUALITY IS A SEED,

00:05:09.100 --> 00:05:10.400
AND THEN RELIGION, YOU KNOW,

00:05:10.400 --> 00:05:12.360
THEY'RE JUST THE
DIFFERENT FLOWERS

00:05:12.360 --> 00:05:14.400
THAT BLOOM WHERE
YOU PLANT THAT SEED.

00:05:14.400 --> 00:05:16.460
SO IF YOU PLANT THE
SEED IN THIS SOCIETY,

00:05:16.460 --> 00:05:17.660
IT'LL BLOOM THIS
WAY, THIS WAY.

00:05:17.660 --> 00:05:20.360
YOU PLANT THE SEED HERE,
IT'LL BLOOM DIFFERENTLY.

00:05:20.360 --> 00:05:26.200
BUT THERE IS A COMMON SEED.

00:05:26.200 --> 00:05:30.830
Malekar: AS BEES TAKE HONEY
FROM DIFFERENT FLOWERS,

00:05:30.830 --> 00:05:34.130
SIMILARLY, A WISE MAN
TAKES A SENSE OF GOODNESS

00:05:34.130 --> 00:05:36.100
FROM EACH AND EVERY RELIGION.

00:05:36.100 --> 00:05:40.630
Fitzgerald: WE HAVE
A COMMON HUMANITY.

00:05:40.630 --> 00:05:42.130
WE BELONG TO DIFFERENT NATIONS.

00:05:42.130 --> 00:05:44.960
WE BELONG TO DIFFERENT
ETHNIC GROUPS,

00:05:44.960 --> 00:05:48.300
AND THE RELIGIONS
ALSO ARE DIFFERENT.

00:05:48.300 --> 00:05:51.600
BUT BASICALLY,
WE ARE ALL HUMAN.

00:05:51.600 --> 00:05:55.360
WE HAVE THE SAME NEEDS. WE
HAVE THE SAME ASPIRATIONS.

00:05:55.360 --> 00:05:58.100
AND WE'RE FACED WITH
THE SAME PROBLEMS.

00:05:58.100 --> 00:05:59.130
[SPEAKING NATIVE LANGUAGE]

00:05:59.130 --> 00:06:01.030
Translator: SO WE
HAVE TO GO BEYOND

00:06:01.030 --> 00:06:02.800
THE CONVENTIONAL
APPROACH TO RELIGION

00:06:02.800 --> 00:06:05.360
TO GET TO THE ROOTS
OF THESE RELIGIONS.

00:06:05.360 --> 00:06:07.830
WE ALL SHARE THE
ONE AND ONLY THING,

00:06:07.830 --> 00:06:11.400
WHICH IS PEACE AND STABILITY
FOR ALL HUMAN BEINGS

00:06:11.400 --> 00:06:14.500
AND FREE WILL FOR ALL HUMANKIND.

00:06:14.500 --> 00:06:18.800
IF YOU LOOK JUST
AT THE DIFFERENCES,

00:06:18.800 --> 00:06:20.860
FORGET WHAT IS PURPOSE.

00:06:20.860 --> 00:06:22.600
[MUSIC PLAYING]

00:06:22.600 --> 00:06:26.200
THERE ARE BIG DIFFERENCES.

00:06:26.200 --> 00:06:30.530
BUT IF YOU LOOK WHAT IS THE
PURPOSE OF THESE TRADITIONS,

00:06:30.530 --> 00:06:34.360
NO MATTER HOW
MANY DIFFERENCES,

00:06:34.360 --> 00:06:36.900
ALL CARRY THE
MESSAGE OF IMPORTANCE

00:06:36.900 --> 00:06:42.560
OF LOVE, COMPASSION,
FORGIVENESS, TOLERANCE.

00:06:42.560 --> 00:06:48.500
THESE ARE FUNDAMENTAL
VALUE OF HUMAN BEING.

00:06:48.500 --> 00:06:51.600
IT BECOMES VERY CLEAR...

00:06:51.600 --> 00:06:56.930
ALL THESE DIFFERENT
PHILOSOPHIES...

00:06:56.930 --> 00:07:00.730
SIMPLY DIFFERENT
WAY OF APPROACH,

00:07:00.730 --> 00:07:03.430
BUT SAME GOAL, SAME MESSAGE--

00:07:03.430 --> 00:07:21.400
TO CREATE BETTER HUMAN BEING.

00:07:21.400 --> 00:07:25.600
PEOPLE HAVE HARMED, OPPRESSED,
AND EVEN EXTERMINATED OTHERS

00:07:25.600 --> 00:07:28.600
IN THE NAME OF GOD.

00:07:28.600 --> 00:07:31.160
HOW IS IT THAT
RELIGION CAN BE USED

00:07:31.160 --> 00:07:33.760
TO JUSTIFY SUCH VIOLENCE?

00:07:33.760 --> 00:07:38.060
Chopra: THERE'S AN EXPRESSION
THAT GOD GAVE HUMANS THE TRUTH,

00:07:38.060 --> 00:07:40.260
AND THEN THE DEVIL SAID,
LET'S ORGANIZE IT.

00:07:40.260 --> 00:07:41.330
WE'LL CALL IT RELIGION.

00:07:41.330 --> 00:07:44.430
IT IS NOT THE RELIGION
THAT HAS CAUSED PROBLEMS.

00:07:44.430 --> 00:07:46.930
IT IS THE PRACTITIONERS
OF RELIGION

00:07:46.930 --> 00:07:48.900
THAT HAS CAUSED PROBLEMS.

00:07:48.900 --> 00:07:51.360
Lhakdor: MANY PEOPLE
SAY THAT RELIGION

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:52.860
IS A SOURCE OF CONFLICT,

00:07:52.860 --> 00:07:55.200
AND PEOPLE FIGHT IN
THE NAME OF RELIGION.

00:07:55.200 --> 00:07:58.560
I WOULD NOT SAY RELIGION ITSELF
IS A SOURCE OF CONFLICT.

00:07:58.560 --> 00:08:00.260
IT IS AGAIN THE HUMAN BEINGS

00:08:00.260 --> 00:08:03.200
WHO ARE THE, REALLY, SOURCE
OF, YOU KNOW, CONFLICT.

00:08:03.200 --> 00:08:05.430
IT REALLY ANGERS ME
BECAUSE OF THE FACT

00:08:05.430 --> 00:08:07.830
THAT THIS HAS NOTHING
TO DO WITH FAITH.

00:08:07.830 --> 00:08:12.130
IT IS LIKE MISUSING THE
GREAT MOTIVATING FORCE

00:08:12.130 --> 00:08:13.300
OF RELIGION.

00:08:13.300 --> 00:08:16.230
THIS IS REALLY THE
VESTED INTEREST

00:08:16.230 --> 00:08:18.600
OF SOME SELF-SEEKING INDIVIDUALS

00:08:18.600 --> 00:08:22.300
WHO ARE MAKING LIFE MISERABLE.

00:08:22.300 --> 00:08:26.330
Armstrong: THERE ARE ALWAYS
PEOPLE IN EVERY RELIGIOUS SYSTEM

00:08:26.330 --> 00:08:28.730
WHO DON'T WANT TO
BE COMPASSIONATE,

00:08:28.730 --> 00:08:30.330
AND THEY WOULD
RATHER BE RIGHT,

00:08:30.330 --> 00:08:34.360
AND THAT'S A GREAT TEMPTATION
FOR RELIGIOUS PEOPLE.

00:08:34.360 --> 00:08:37.060
AND ANYBODY WHO
DOESN'T AGREE WITH YOU,

00:08:37.060 --> 00:08:38.230
THEN THEY'RE OUTSIDE,

00:08:38.230 --> 00:08:41.830
THEY'RE CAST OUT
INTO OUTER DARKNESS,

00:08:41.830 --> 00:08:44.360
AND YOU WON'T HAVE
ANYTHING TO DO WITH THEM

00:08:44.360 --> 00:08:46.200
AND YOU FIGHT AGAINST THEM,

00:08:46.200 --> 00:08:48.060
AND THAT'S REALLY NOT THE WAY

00:08:48.060 --> 00:08:50.400
GOD CREATED THE
WORLD, I THINK.

00:08:50.400 --> 00:08:55.300
WE ARE CALLED TO HAVE
A MUCH BROADER VIEW.

00:08:55.300 --> 00:08:59.130
YOU KNOW, IF YOU SAY GOD
IS LOVE, FOR EXAMPLE,

00:08:59.130 --> 00:09:03.830
THEN YOU CAN'T SAY, WELL,
LOVE IS ONLY FROM ISRAEL,

00:09:03.830 --> 00:09:06.330
OR LOVE IS ONLY FROM
FRANCE, OR LOVE...

00:09:06.330 --> 00:09:09.000
I MEAN, EVERY BEING...
LOVE IS ALL OVER THE WORLD.

00:09:09.000 --> 00:09:11.700
LOVE IS EVERYWHERE. LOVE
IS THE LOGOS, YOU KNOW.

00:09:11.700 --> 00:09:13.400
IT'S IN THE ATOMS
OF THE UNIVERSE.

00:09:13.400 --> 00:09:15.830
SO PEOPLE WHO TRY TO,
LIKE, GRAB IT AND OWN IT

00:09:15.830 --> 00:09:18.130
AND SAY THAT NOBODY ELSE HAS IT

00:09:18.130 --> 00:09:20.200
ARE THE PROBLEM
HERE, YOU KNOW.

00:09:20.200 --> 00:09:24.860
[PEOPLE CHANTING]

00:09:24.860 --> 00:09:28.700
Jones: YOU KNOW, THIS QUEST
FOR CERTAINTY IS SO DANGEROUS.

00:09:28.700 --> 00:09:32.300
YOU KNOW, I KNOW
MY DOCTRINE IS CORRECT,
AND THAT'S MY FAITH.

00:09:32.300 --> 00:09:33.460
NO, NO, NO, NO.

00:09:33.460 --> 00:09:35.360
FAITH IS STANDING
IN THE MYSTERY.

00:09:35.360 --> 00:09:39.500
FAITH IS BEING COMPLETELY
BAFFLED BY THE MYSTERY

00:09:39.500 --> 00:09:42.430
AND YET STILL BELIEVING
INSIDE YOURSELF

00:09:42.430 --> 00:09:44.630
THAT THERE'S A UNIVERSE
WORKING FOR GOOD

00:09:44.630 --> 00:09:47.260
AND THAT'S THERE'S A
PURPOSE FOR YOUR LIFE

00:09:47.260 --> 00:09:49.260
AND THAT YOU'LL
FIND THAT PURPOSE

00:09:49.260 --> 00:09:51.500
THE MORE YOU SURRENDER
TO THAT MYSTERY,

00:09:51.500 --> 00:09:55.300
NOT TO THE CERTAINTY.
THAT'S FAITH.

00:09:55.300 --> 00:10:03.630
YOU KNOW, THERE IS A SAYING
OF A GREAT MUSLIM MYSTIC,

00:10:03.630 --> 00:10:06.900
JALALUDDIN RUMI, WHO SAID,

00:10:06.900 --> 00:10:13.960
I WENT TO THE CHURCH SEEKING
GOD, AND I DIDN'T FIND IT.

00:10:13.960 --> 00:10:16.200
THEN I WENT TO SYNAGOGUE,

00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:20.230
AND I DID NOT FIND
GOD EITHER THERE.

00:10:20.230 --> 00:10:23.560
AND THEN I WENT
TO THE MOSQUE,

00:10:23.560 --> 00:10:27.460
AND I DID NOT FIND GOD
IN THE MOSQUE EITHER.

00:10:27.460 --> 00:11:02.960
I CAME HOME, AND I
FOUND GOD IN MY HEART.

00:11:02.960 --> 00:11:08.200
Chopra: BECAUSE THE SPIRITUAL
EXPERIENCE IS SO INTOXICATING

00:11:08.200 --> 00:11:11.700
AND BECAUSE IT'S SO MEANINGFUL

00:11:11.700 --> 00:11:15.730
AND BECAUSE WE ALL
SO YEARN FOR IT,

00:11:15.730 --> 00:11:18.730
IF WE DON'T HAVE THE
DIRECT EXPERIENCE OURSELF,

00:11:18.730 --> 00:11:21.230
WE LOOK TO AUTHORITIES.

00:11:21.230 --> 00:11:23.860
I DON'T THINK CHRIST
WAS A CHRISTIAN

00:11:23.860 --> 00:11:25.600
OR THAT BUDDHA WAS A BUDDHIST.

00:11:25.600 --> 00:11:28.400
THESE ARE WORDS THAT
WE CREATED LATER.

00:11:28.400 --> 00:11:32.200
WE TOOK AN EXPERIENCE,
SOMEBODY ELSE'S EXPERIENCE,

00:11:32.200 --> 00:11:36.100
AND WE BELIEVED IN IT,
AND THEN WE CREATED

00:11:36.100 --> 00:11:38.230
DOGMA AND IDEOLOGY AROUND IT.

00:11:38.230 --> 00:11:42.530
YOU KNOW, MY GOD IS
BETTER THAN YOUR GOD.

00:11:42.530 --> 00:11:50.700
THEN WE GO TO WAR TO DEFEND IT.

00:11:50.700 --> 00:11:54.360
BECAUSE RELIGION SEEKS TO
GIVE MEANING TO OUR LIVES,

00:11:54.360 --> 00:11:56.830
IT'S BOUND UP WITH
ALL THE COMPONENTS

00:11:56.830 --> 00:11:58.900
OF OUR UNDERSTANDING
OF WHO WE ARE

00:11:58.900 --> 00:12:01.360
AS INDIVIDUALS, AS
MEMBERS OF FAMILIES,

00:12:01.360 --> 00:12:03.760
AS COMMUNITIES, AS
NATIONS, PEOPLES,

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:12.400
EVEN AS PART OF
THE WHOLE COSMOS.

00:12:12.400 --> 00:12:16.560
THE SOURCES OF PEOPLE'S
VIOLENT BEHAVIOR

00:12:16.560 --> 00:12:22.530
ARE ALWAYS SOME
FORM OF ALIENATION.

00:12:22.530 --> 00:12:25.630
IN SOME SENSE, THAT
SOCIETY LOOKS DOWN ON YOU

00:12:25.630 --> 00:12:28.060
OR EVEN HUMILIATES YOU.

00:12:28.060 --> 00:12:30.360
YOU OFTEN SEE
RELIGION BEING USED

00:12:30.360 --> 00:12:32.800
TO STRENGTHEN THE
SENSE OF IDENTITY

00:12:32.800 --> 00:12:35.160
OF THOSE WHO FEEL THAT
THEY'RE BEING ATTACKED.

00:12:35.160 --> 00:12:38.460
MOST OF THE SO-CALLED
FUNDAMENTALIST MOVEMENTS

00:12:38.460 --> 00:12:41.060
IN RELIGIOUS TERMS SPRING FROM

00:12:41.060 --> 00:12:43.760
THIS KIND OF FEAR
OF ANNIHILATION

00:12:43.760 --> 00:12:48.160
OR THE DESIRE TO ASSERT
A CLEAR IDENTITY.

00:12:48.160 --> 00:12:51.630
AND THEREFORE TO SEE YOURSELF AS
THE GODLY AGAINST THE GODLESS

00:12:51.630 --> 00:12:54.560
AND TO SEE YOURSELF
IN AN INEXORABLE WAR

00:12:54.560 --> 00:12:56.530
BETWEEN THE GOOD
AGAINST THE EVIL.

00:12:56.530 --> 00:12:59.060
WHEN THE CRUSADERS
WENT INTO BATTLE

00:12:59.060 --> 00:13:04.430
TO KILL JEWS AND MUSLIMS,
THEY CRIED, GOD WILLS IT!

00:13:04.430 --> 00:13:05.930
THAT WAS THEIR BATTLE CRY.

00:13:05.930 --> 00:13:10.360
THERE'S ALWAYS BEEN
A DANGER OF USING GOD

00:13:10.360 --> 00:13:19.230
TO ENDORSE SOME OF OUR WORST
FEARS, HATREDS, AND PREJUDICES.

00:13:19.230 --> 00:13:24.930
BECAUSE ONCE YOU TOUCH
RELIGION, FAITH,

00:13:24.930 --> 00:13:27.600
IT'S FILLED WITH EMOTION.

00:13:27.600 --> 00:13:29.760
SO EASY MANIPULATED.

00:13:29.760 --> 00:13:32.030
WHEN PEOPLE HURT
IN THE NAME OF GOD,

00:13:32.030 --> 00:13:36.400
I CAN'T QUITE UNDERSTAND
BECAUSE IN MY OPINION,

00:13:36.400 --> 00:13:38.030
GOD IS LOVE.

00:13:38.030 --> 00:13:41.560
PROBABLY...IF YOU
ARE FIGHTING FOR GOD,

00:13:41.560 --> 00:13:44.830
I'M ASKING TO MYSELF,
IS THIS PERSON

00:13:44.830 --> 00:13:48.600
TRYING TO CONVINCE
HIM- OR HERSELF

00:13:48.600 --> 00:13:50.860
THAT THEY HAVE FAITH?

00:13:50.860 --> 00:13:52.460
Armstrong: ONCE YOU SAY

00:13:52.460 --> 00:13:55.400
THAT IT'S RIGHT TO KILL
IN THE NAME OF GOD,

00:13:55.400 --> 00:13:58.860
YOU HAVE LOST THE PLOT
IN RELIGIOUS TERMS.

00:13:58.860 --> 00:14:00.400
ALL THE RELIGIONS TEACH

00:14:00.400 --> 00:14:03.600
THAT STOPPING VIOLENCE
AS SOON AS POSSIBLE

00:14:03.600 --> 00:14:06.500
IS ABSOLUTELY CRUCIAL
AND THAT HUMAN LIFE,

00:14:06.500 --> 00:14:09.100
EVEN THE HUMAN LIFE
OF OUR ENEMIES,

00:14:09.100 --> 00:14:13.500
IS ABSOLUTELY SACRED
AND INVALUABLE.

00:14:13.500 --> 00:14:16.800
TO SAY THAT IT'S RIGHT TO
KILL IN THE NAME OF GOD

00:14:16.800 --> 00:14:17.860
IS A HERESY.

00:14:17.860 --> 00:14:22.660
THE MOST FERVENT BELIEVERS
ARE FUNDAMENTALISTS,

00:14:22.660 --> 00:14:32.230
AND LOOK WHAT THEY'VE
DONE TO THE WORLD.

00:14:32.230 --> 00:14:36.330
Narrator: AFTER YEARS
OF RUSSIAN OCCUPATION
AND CIVIL WAR,

00:14:36.330 --> 00:14:38.330
A RELIGIOUS PARTY
CALLED THE TALIBAN

00:14:38.330 --> 00:14:43.030
TOOK CONTROL OF
AFGHANISTAN IN 1995.

00:14:43.030 --> 00:14:45.160
THIS FUNDAMENTALIST
SECT BELIEVED IN

00:14:45.160 --> 00:14:48.060
THE STRICT ENFORCEMENT
OF ISLAMIC LAW

00:14:48.060 --> 00:14:49.730
AS THEY INTERPRETED IT.

00:14:49.730 --> 00:14:53.100
THEY PREVENTED GIRLS
FROM GOING TO SCHOOL.

00:14:53.100 --> 00:14:54.860
THEY BARRED WOMEN FROM WORKING

00:14:54.860 --> 00:14:57.600
AND PROHIBITED THEM FROM
APPEARING IN PUBLIC

00:14:57.600 --> 00:15:08.400
WITHOUT A MALE RELATIVE.

00:15:08.400 --> 00:15:12.300
SHUKRIA BARAKZAI, A
DEVOUT MUSLIM WOMAN,

00:15:12.300 --> 00:15:29.130
REFUSED TO OBEY THE TALIBAN'S
RESTRICTIONS ON HER FREEDOM.

00:15:29.130 --> 00:15:31.730
Barakzai: I REMEMBER
THE TALIBAN,

00:15:31.730 --> 00:15:35.400
THEY BEAT ME IN THE
STREET. FOR WHAT?

00:15:35.400 --> 00:15:38.630
BECAUSE THEY DIDN'T LIKE WOMEN.

00:15:38.630 --> 00:15:44.430
I WAS JUST WENT TO THE
DOCTOR. I WAS SICK.

00:15:44.430 --> 00:15:45.730
I WEAR THE BURQA.

