I FEEL MYSELF, AS A
RESPONSIBLE AFGHAN,

00:16:40.460 --> 00:16:44.360
AS AN INDIVIDUAL,
TO FIGHT FOR THAT,

00:16:44.360 --> 00:16:49.500
TO DO SOMETHING FOR THE FUTURE.

