WHEN I'M ASKING
WOMEN'S RIGHTS,

00:18:05.560 --> 00:18:09.960
IT'S DIRECT CONNECTION WITH
ISLAM, WITH MY RELIGION.

00:18:09.960 --> 00:18:14.200
WHY ISLAM WOMEN HAVE
RIGHTS OF EDUCATION.

00:18:14.200 --> 00:18:18.100
ISLAM NEVER MEANS
LACK OF FREEDOM.

00:18:18.100 --> 00:18:25.700
ISLAM MEANS RESPECT,
RESPECT EACH OTHER.

00:18:25.700 --> 00:18:29.700
FOR ME, GOD MEANS LOVE.

00:18:29.700 --> 00:18:32.230
I LOVE MY GOD.

00:18:32.230 --> 00:18:34.730
I BELIEVE HIM.

00:18:34.730 --> 00:18:45.760
HE PROTECTS ME ALWAYS.

