THAT SOMEBODY WOULD
BE EXCLUDED FROM

00:24:26.530 --> 00:24:28.600
THE CIRCLE OF FORGIVENESS
AND REDEMPTION,

00:24:28.600 --> 00:24:32.200
TO ME, THAT WAS WHAT IT WAS ALL
