00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:35.230
I THOUGHT A REAL
EXTENSION OF MY OWN FAITH

00:24:35.230 --> 00:24:37.760
WAS TO DO THIS WORK
OF HELPING THE PEOPLE

00:24:37.760 --> 00:24:39.700
WHO HAVE BEEN PUT BEHIND BARS.

00:24:39.700 --> 00:24:42.030
WHAT IF THE SOCIETY
REALLY RECOGNIZED

00:24:42.030 --> 00:24:44.330
THAT THE REAL
POWER OF, YOU KNOW,

00:24:44.330 --> 00:24:45.560
WHEN PEOPLE DO HIT BOTTOM,

