THAT THAT'S THE BEST
POSSIBLE MOMENT IN SOME WAYS

00:24:49.860 --> 00:24:52.630
TO HELP THAT PERSON TO
REBOUND, TO RECOVER,

00:24:52.630 --> 00:24:55.330
AND TO THINK ABOUT
THE GIFTS TO SOCIETY

