INSTEAD WE SAY, THAT
WORST POSSIBLE MOMENT

00:24:58.660 --> 00:25:00.330
IS JUST THE BEGINNING
OF BAD MOMENTS FOR YOU,

00:25:00.330 --> 00:25:02.360
BECAUSE WE'RE GOING
TO MAKE IT WORSE FOR YOU

00:25:02.360 --> 00:25:10.160
AND WORSE FOR YOU
AND WORSE FOR YOU.

