OR ANY THROWAWAY NEIGHBORHOODS

00:25:15.330 --> 00:25:18.630
OR ANY THROWAWAY NATIONS
OR CONTINENTS OR SPECIES.

00:25:18.630 --> 00:25:20.000
I THINK IT'S ALL PRECIOUS,

00:25:20.000 --> 00:25:23.460
AND, YOU KNOW, FOR ME, THAT'S
THE GROUNDING OF MY FAITH,

00:25:23.460 --> 00:25:24.660
THAT IT'S ALL SACRED.

00:25:24.660 --> 00:25:26.930
YOU KNOW, THE CREATOR
MADE ALL OF THIS,

00:25:26.930 --> 00:25:29.500
AND OUR CHALLENGE IS TO
SEE THE CREATOR'S FACE,

