AND SO I JUST FEEL
LIKE, IN SOME WAYS,

00:27:36.030 --> 00:27:39.260
YOU GUYS ARE REALLY
ON THE LEADING EDGE

00:27:39.260 --> 00:27:41.360
OF WHAT WE'RE TALKING ABOUT,

