BECAUSE TO BE ABLE TO ACHIEVE
WHAT YOU'RE ACHIEVING,

00:27:45.660 --> 00:27:47.330
THAT SPIRITUAL DOMAIN,

00:27:47.330 --> 00:27:50.700
WHEN SOCIETY WOULD SAY, WELL,
THIS WOULD BE THE WORST PLACE.

