OR WHO HAVE DIED AT THE
HANDS OF EACH OTHER,

00:28:09.660 --> 00:28:12.330
YOU KNOW, YOU BEGIN
TO REALLY GET A SENSE

00:28:12.330 --> 00:28:13.630
OF HOW PRECIOUS LIFE IS.

