IF PEOPLE OUTSIDE
COULD SEE THIS,

00:28:15.000 --> 00:28:17.660
I THINK WE MIGHT BE A LITTLE
BIT MORE WILLING TO FORGIVE,

00:28:17.660 --> 00:28:26.760
TO THINK ABOUT HOW WE MIGHT
MAKE A BRIDGE BACK HOME.

