00:31:09.130 --> 00:31:13.160
BECAUSE YOU CANNOT HAVE VIOLENCE

00:31:13.160 --> 00:31:17.530
AND NOT HAVE BITTERNESS.

00:31:17.530 --> 00:31:22.430
HE SAID THAT HIS
LIFE WAS HIS MESSAGE.

