ONCE THEY ASKED
MAHATMA GANDHI,

00:31:40.100 --> 00:31:45.330
WHAT'S THE MOST IMPORTANT
QUALITY IN SPIRITUALITY?

00:31:45.330 --> 00:31:50.600
AND MAHATMA GANDHI
SAID, NOT BE COWARD.

00:31:50.600 --> 00:31:53.330
I THINK THE MOST
IMPORTANT QUALITY

00:31:53.330 --> 00:32:00.130
THAT A MAN OR A WOMAN
SHOULD HAVE IS TO BE BRAVE.

00:32:00.130 --> 00:32:03.060
Narrator: THE REVEREND
MARTIN LUTHER KING, JR.

00:32:03.060 --> 00:32:05.330
BASED THE AMERICAN
CIVIL RIGHTS MOVEMENT

00:32:05.330 --> 00:32:08.860
ON THE TEACHINGS OF THE
HINDU MAHATMA GANDHI.

00:32:08.860 --> 00:32:11.030
THE BAPTIST MINISTER
FROM ATLANTA, GEORGIA,

00:32:11.030 --> 00:32:15.630
SAW THAT LOVE AND RESPECT COULD
SET BLACK AND WHITE AMERICANS

00:32:15.630 --> 00:32:19.230
FREE OF THEIR RACIST HISTORY.

00:32:19.230 --> 00:32:22.830
Young: GANDHI'S
UNDERSTANDING OF CHRISTIANITY

00:32:22.830 --> 00:32:25.560
WAS MORE RELEVANT TO ME

00:32:25.560 --> 00:32:27.430
THAN THE UNDERSTANDING
OF CHRISTIANITY

00:32:27.430 --> 00:32:30.700
THAT I GOT FROM MOST
U.S. CHRISTIANS,

00:32:30.700 --> 00:32:34.900
AND PARTICULARLY THE IDEA
OF LOVING YOUR ENEMY.

00:32:34.900 --> 00:32:38.160
I'D NEVER HEARD
ANYBODY IN THE U.S.

00:32:38.160 --> 00:32:39.860
TAKE THAT SERIOUSLY HARDLY.

00:32:39.860 --> 00:32:43.330
LOVE YOUR ENEMY AND BLESS
THOSE THAT PERSECUTE YOU.

00:32:43.330 --> 00:32:47.560
THERE WEREN'T MANY
PEOPLE THAT WERE TALKING

00:32:47.560 --> 00:32:49.330
NONVIOLENT SOCIAL CHANGE.

00:32:49.330 --> 00:32:55.130
AND THERE WAS STILL A
TREMENDOUS AMOUNT OF DOUBT,

00:32:55.130 --> 00:32:58.500
I DIDN'T THINK NONVIOLENCE
WOULD WORK IN THE SOUTH,

00:32:58.500 --> 00:33:02.000
THAT AMERICA WAS TOO
VIOLENT AND TOO MILITARIST

00:33:02.000 --> 00:33:04.960
TO RESPOND TO THIS.

00:33:04.960 --> 00:33:08.730
FREDERICK DOUGLASS SAID THAT
THE STRUGGLE FOR FREEDOM

00:33:08.730 --> 00:33:12.730
IS A STRUGGLE TO SAVE
BLACK MEN'S BODIES

00:33:12.730 --> 00:33:16.630
AND WHITE MEN'S SOULS.

00:33:16.630 --> 00:33:19.360
RACISM IS A SICKNESS,

00:33:19.360 --> 00:33:22.000
AND YOU DON'T GET
ANGRY WITH SICK PEOPLE.

00:33:22.000 --> 00:33:23.760
YOU HELP THEM AND HEAL THEM.

00:33:23.760 --> 00:33:25.600
AND HEALING WAS SPIRITUAL.

00:33:25.600 --> 00:33:27.960
AND NONVIOLENCE
THEN SEEMED TO BE

00:33:27.960 --> 00:33:29.960
A SPIRITUAL METHOD OF HEALING.

00:33:29.960 --> 00:33:33.330
THAT WAS THE FIRST TIME I
UNDERSTOOD THAT RELIGION

00:33:33.330 --> 00:33:36.760
HAD THE CAPACITY
TO CHANGE PEOPLE,

00:33:36.760 --> 00:33:40.460
AND IF YOU CAN CHANGE PEOPLE,
YOU CAN CHANGE SOCIETY.

00:33:40.460 --> 00:33:45.160
King, Jr.: THE AFTERMATH OF
NONVIOLENCE IS THE CREATION

00:33:45.160 --> 00:33:46.600
OF THE BELOVED COMMUNITY.

00:33:46.600 --> 00:33:50.930
THE AFTERMATH OF
NONVIOLENCE IS REDEMPTION.

00:33:50.930 --> 00:33:54.030
WE MUST COME TO
THE POINT OF SEEING

00:33:54.030 --> 00:33:58.430
THAT OUR ULTIMATE AIM
IS TO LIVE WITH ALL MEN

00:33:58.430 --> 00:34:01.000
AS BROTHERS AND
SISTERS UNDER GOD

00:34:01.000 --> 00:34:04.760
AND NOT BE THEIR ENEMIES.

00:34:04.760 --> 00:34:08.760
Young: MARTIN USED TO SAY
THAT LIFE IS ABOUT COMMITMENT

00:34:08.760 --> 00:34:10.300
TO YOUR OWN BELIEFS,

00:34:10.300 --> 00:34:12.530
AND IF YOU'RE COMMITTED
TO THOSE BELIEFS

00:34:12.530 --> 00:34:14.200
AND ARE WILLING TO WORK HARD,

00:34:14.200 --> 00:34:16.600
SACRIFICE, SUFFER,
AND BE SENSITIVE

00:34:16.600 --> 00:34:19.100
TO THE PEOPLE WHO
DISAGREE WITH YOU,

00:34:19.100 --> 00:34:31.760
THEN THERE'S ALMOST
NOTHING THAT CAN'T BE DONE.

00:34:31.760 --> 00:34:35.800
[SHOUTING]

