AND THERE'S NO WAY,

00:35:15.600 --> 00:35:17.630
DESPITE ALL APPEARANCES
TO THE CONTRARY,

00:35:17.630 --> 00:35:25.030
THERE'S NO WAY IN WHICH EVIL
WILL HAVE THE LAST WORD.

00:35:25.030 --> 00:35:31.160
AND WE REALIZED THAT THE HEALING
COULD ULTIMATELY ACTUALLY HAPPEN

00:35:31.160 --> 00:35:38.500
ONLY THROUGH THOSE WHO
WERE THEMSELVES WOUNDED.

