IS BY CONFESSING.

00:36:03.600 --> 00:36:05.660
[HORNS HONKING AND
PEOPLE CHEERING]

00:36:05.660 --> 00:36:10.560
PEOPLE ARE A GLORIOUS CREATION.

00:36:10.560 --> 00:36:16.730
JUST AS MUCH AS WE
HAVE THIS EXTRAORDINARY
CAPACITY FOR EVIL,

00:36:16.730 --> 00:36:22.630
SO WE HAVE A REMARKABLE
CAPACITY FOR GOOD.

00:36:22.630 --> 00:36:30.360
EACH ONE OF US HAS THE
CAPACITY TO BECOME A SAINT.

00:36:30.360 --> 00:36:32.130
INCREDIBLE.

00:36:32.130 --> 00:36:33.200
[LOUD VOICES]

00:36:33.200 --> 00:36:38.000
WE FOLLOW THE ONE WHO SAYS,
FORGIVE ONE ANOTHER

00:36:38.000 --> 00:36:42.030
AS GOD IN CHRIST
FORGAVE YOU.

00:36:42.030 --> 00:36:47.360
THERE IS NO SITUATION
ANYWHERE IN THE WORLD

00:36:47.360 --> 00:36:50.800
THAT IS NOT TRANSFIGURABLE.

00:36:50.800 --> 00:36:56.700
THERE IS NOBODY IN THE WORLD
WHO IS BEYOND THE PAIN.

00:36:56.700 --> 00:37:01.500
WE ARE FAMILY. SOME ARE
LIGHT IN COMPLEXION,

00:37:01.500 --> 00:37:04.930
OTHERS DARK, RIGHT
AROUND THE WORLD,

00:37:04.930 --> 00:37:09.130
AND GOD'S DREAM IS THAT
ONE DAY WE WILL WAKE UP

00:37:09.130 --> 00:37:30.600
TO THIS FUNDAMENTAL
TRUTH ABOUT US.

