DO NOT DEVELOP HATRED
TOWARDS THE PERSON.

00:38:41.830 --> 00:38:46.860
ON THAT BASIS, TO
DEVELOP FORGIVENESS.

00:38:46.860 --> 00:38:51.400
[APPLAUSE]

