Translator: IN A WORLD
IN WHICH SUSPICION

00:39:01.100 --> 00:39:04.430
AND AGGRESSION HAVE ALL TOO
LONG CHARACTERIZED RELATIONS

00:39:04.430 --> 00:39:06.400
BETWEEN PEOPLES AND NATIONS...

