ONLY LOVE CAN PUT
AN END TO HATRED,

00:40:52.630 --> 00:40:54.930
AND ONLY NONVIOLENCE
AND GENTLENESS

00:40:54.930 --> 00:40:56.660
CAN PUT AN END TO VIOLENCE.

00:40:56.660 --> 00:41:02.360
IF YOU GIVE INTO ANGER AND
HATRED AND COMMIT VIOLENCE,

00:41:02.360 --> 00:41:06.160
THE ONE WHO IS MOST
VIOLATED IS YOURSELF.

00:41:06.160 --> 00:41:08.160
BY SURRENDERING TO
ANGER AND HATRED,

00:41:08.160 --> 00:41:10.560
YOU ARE ALLOWING
IT TO VIOLATE YOU.

00:41:10.560 --> 00:41:14.460
Translator: VIOLENT
METHODS NOT ONLY FAILED

