AND RELIGION HAS A UNIQUE
ROLE TO PLAY IN THAT REGARD,

00:42:25.400 --> 00:42:27.830
AND THAT'S WHY WE NEED TO
SEE THOSE RELIGIOUS VOICES

00:42:27.830 --> 00:42:30.600
MUCH MORE CENTRALLY
ENGAGED IN A PROCESS

00:42:30.600 --> 00:42:39.360
OF RECONCILIATION
AND PEACEMAKING.

