Habash: WE HAVE TO REALLY
START TRANSLATING FAITH

01:00:42.830 --> 01:00:48.160
AND SPIRITUALITY AND RELIGION
INTO PRACTICAL ACTIONS.

01:00:48.160 --> 01:00:50.660
WE CANNOT CONTINUE
PRAYING TO GOD

01:00:50.660 --> 01:00:53.000
AND THEN NOT DOING ANYTHING.

01:00:53.000 --> 01:00:57.630
Vahedi: IF I TRY TO PUT INTO
PRACTICE WHAT I BELIEVE,

01:00:57.630 --> 01:01:01.560
THAT IS GOING TO BRING
ABOUT A POSITIVE CHANGE,

01:01:01.560 --> 01:01:03.430
MAKE THIS WORLD
A BETTER WORLD,

01:01:03.430 --> 01:01:06.530
NO MATTER WHERE I AM,
AND I THINK THAT IS

01:01:06.530 --> 01:01:09.630
THE GREATEST THING THAT
CAN HAPPEN IN OUR LIFE,

01:01:09.630 --> 01:01:21.200
AND IT IS HAPPENING IN THE
LIFE OF SO MANY PEOPLE.

01:01:21.200 --> 01:01:23.430
Narrator: FATHER
KIERAN CREAGH,

01:01:23.430 --> 01:01:25.560
A MISSIONARY PRIEST
FROM NORTHERN IRELAND,

01:01:25.560 --> 01:01:29.330
MINISTERS TO THE PEOPLE OF
ATTERIDGEVILLE, SOUTH AFRICA.

01:01:29.330 --> 01:01:32.630
IT WAS THERE HE FIRST
SAW THE HARSH REALITY

01:01:32.630 --> 01:01:34.130
OF THE A.I.D.S. EPIDEMIC

01:01:34.130 --> 01:01:37.560
AND FELT COMPELLED TO ACT.

01:01:37.560 --> 01:01:39.360
Creagh: I WAS
WORKING AS A PRIEST

01:01:39.360 --> 01:01:44.760
HERE IN THE TOWNSHIP AT
ATTERIDGEVILLE FOR A FEW YEARS.

01:01:44.760 --> 01:01:46.860
AND AS A PRIEST,
YOU'D BE CALLED OUT

01:01:46.860 --> 01:01:48.560
WHEN PEOPLE WOULD
BE AT THEIR WORST,

01:01:48.560 --> 01:01:49.830
WHEN THE DOCTORS
COULD DO NO MORE,

01:01:49.830 --> 01:01:51.730
THE SANGOMAS COULD DO NO
MORE THAN MAYBE TO SAY,

01:01:51.730 --> 01:01:55.400
WELL, AT LEAST CALL THE
PRIEST TO DO THE LAST PRAYERS

01:01:55.400 --> 01:01:56.900
OR MAYBE A BIT OF HEALING.

01:01:56.900 --> 01:02:00.830
AND ONE DAY I WAS CALLED
OUT TO A GUY CALLED RONALD,

01:02:00.830 --> 01:02:04.600
A 50-YEAR-OLD MAN, AND
I WAS JUST APPALLED

01:02:04.600 --> 01:02:06.000
AT THE CONDITION HE WAS IN.

01:02:06.000 --> 01:02:07.930
HE WAS DYING OF A.I.D.S.,
AND HIS WIFE WAS

01:02:07.930 --> 01:02:10.000
THE ONLY ONE ABLE
TO LOOK AFTER HIM,

01:02:10.000 --> 01:02:12.030
AND SHE ALSO HAD A.I.D.S.,

01:02:12.030 --> 01:02:14.160
AND THEY HAD NO RUNNING
WATER, NO ELECTRICITY,

01:02:14.160 --> 01:02:18.060
AND THE HEAT AND THE SMELL
IN THE SHACK WAS DREADFUL.

01:02:18.060 --> 01:02:20.700
AND I JUST THOUGHT,

01:02:20.700 --> 01:02:22.930
WHERE'S MOTHER TERESA
WHEN YOU NEED HER?

01:02:22.930 --> 01:02:24.060
SHE SHOULD BE HERE.

01:02:24.060 --> 01:02:25.330
OR SOMEBODY SHOULD BE HERE.

01:02:25.330 --> 01:02:27.460
SOMEBODY NEEDS TO DO
SOMETHING ABOUT THIS.

01:02:27.460 --> 01:02:29.630
AND I JUST GOT A
VOICE BACK SAYING,

01:02:29.630 --> 01:02:31.030
WELL, YOU DO
SOMETHING ABOUT IT.

01:02:31.030 --> 01:02:36.160
SO I DECIDED, WELL,
MAYBE THAT'S A CALL
THAT I NEED TO ANSWER.

01:02:36.160 --> 01:02:47.060
AND I THOUGHT, WELL,
LET'S TRY IT OUT.

01:02:47.060 --> 01:02:51.460
WE OPENED OUR DOORS ON
THE FIRST OF JULY, 2004.

01:02:51.460 --> 01:02:57.060
AND SINCE THEN, WE'VE
TAKEN IN 306 PATIENTS,

01:02:57.060 --> 01:03:02.200
MAINLY H.I.V. AND A.I.D.S.
RELATED ILLNESSES.

01:03:02.200 --> 01:03:05.060
THE NAME OF OUR HOSPICE
IS CALLED LERATONG,

01:03:05.060 --> 01:03:09.760
AND LERATONG IS A
SESOTHO WORD THAT MEANS
THE PLACE OF LOVE.

01:03:09.760 --> 01:03:12.130
MY BELIEF IS THAT GOD IS LOVE,

01:03:12.130 --> 01:03:14.160
SO THIS IS THE PLACE OF GOD.

01:03:14.160 --> 01:03:16.460
YOU'RE DOING WELL?

01:03:16.460 --> 01:03:18.160
AND THAT'S WHAT I WANT
PEOPLE TO EXPERIENCE.

01:03:18.160 --> 01:03:21.760
I MEAN, THEY COME HERE, THEY
COME TO A SPIRITUAL PLACE,

01:03:21.760 --> 01:03:23.930
A GOOD PLACE, A LOVING PLACE.

01:03:23.930 --> 01:03:24.830
OK.

01:03:24.830 --> 01:03:26.500
[SPEAKING NATIVE LANGUAGE]

01:03:26.500 --> 01:03:29.500
I LOVE YOU, TOO. HA HA HA!

01:03:29.500 --> 01:03:32.360
HELLO. WHAT KIND OF
PLACE IS THIS WITH CAKE?

01:03:32.360 --> 01:03:35.800
WHERE PEOPLE COME TOGETHER,
THAT'S WHERE GOD IS.

01:03:35.800 --> 01:03:37.330
OK, LISTEN, ENJOY YOUR CAKE.

01:03:37.330 --> 01:03:39.160
I'LL SEE YOU LATER ON.

01:03:39.160 --> 01:03:50.330
THANK YOU.

01:03:50.330 --> 01:03:53.500
Narrator: IN 2003,
FATHER CREAGH WAS

01:03:53.500 --> 01:03:55.100
THE FIRST PERSON IN AFRICA

01:03:55.100 --> 01:03:58.860
TO BE INJECTED WITH
THE A.I.D.S. VACCINE.

01:03:58.860 --> 01:04:01.130
Creagh: I HAVE BEEN WORKING
WITH THE YOUNG PEOPLE HERE

01:04:01.130 --> 01:04:04.030
IN THE TOWNSHIP TO HELP THEM
CHANGE THEIR BEHAVIORS,

01:04:04.030 --> 01:04:06.460
TO GET THEM TO STOP
SLEEPING AROUND

01:04:06.460 --> 01:04:08.600
OR TO HAVING SEX BEFORE MARRIAGE

01:04:08.600 --> 01:04:12.330
SO THEY WOULDN'T
BE GETTING A.I.D.S.

01:04:12.330 --> 01:04:14.630
FOR SOME REASON, THE MESSAGE
WASN'T GETTING THROUGH.

01:04:14.630 --> 01:04:18.800
SO I THOUGHT, WELL, IF IT
MAKES SOME PEOPLE THINK,

01:04:18.800 --> 01:04:20.800
WELL, IF THAT
CHAP CAN DO THAT,

01:04:20.800 --> 01:04:22.460
THEN MAYBE I CAN ABSTAIN,

01:04:22.460 --> 01:04:26.030
OR I CAN CHANGE MY BEHAVIOR.

01:04:26.030 --> 01:04:29.500
IF THIS WILL STOP PEOPLE FROM
GETTING H.I.V. AND A.I.D.S.,

01:04:29.500 --> 01:04:31.460
THEN IT'S A GOOD THING TO DO.

01:04:31.460 --> 01:04:34.700
I THINK GOD IS GREATER AND
BIGGER AND MORE WONDERFUL

01:04:34.700 --> 01:04:38.400
AND MORE FANTASTIC THAN
ANY OF US WILL EVER KNOW.

01:04:38.400 --> 01:04:41.560
I THINK SOMETIMES
RELIGIOUS PRACTICE

01:04:41.560 --> 01:04:43.400
CAN GET IN THE WAY.

01:04:43.400 --> 01:04:45.260
PEOPLE WILL TELL
YOU HOW TO FIND GOD

01:04:45.260 --> 01:04:47.130
OR WHAT YOU HAVE
TO DO TO GET GOD.

01:04:47.130 --> 01:04:48.760
IT'S LIKE YOU HAVE TO WIN GOD.

01:04:48.760 --> 01:04:52.830
RELIGIOUS PRACTICE IS GREAT IF
IT'S DONE FROM A GOOD HEART.

01:04:52.830 --> 01:04:58.630
BUT ANYTHING ELSE, ANY LESS,
IS JUST LIKE ST. PAUL SAYS,

01:04:58.630 --> 01:05:02.330
A BOOM CLASHING,
A GONG BANGING.

01:05:02.330 --> 01:05:03.600
IT'S NO PROBLEM?

01:05:03.600 --> 01:05:05.760
I NEVER FIND GOD IN A CHURCH.

01:05:05.760 --> 01:05:07.830
IN OUR LANGUAGE, IN
THE IRISH LANGUAGE,

01:05:07.830 --> 01:05:09.730
THE WORD FOR A CHURCH IS
TEACH AN PHOBAIL,

01:05:09.730 --> 01:05:13.230
WHICH TRANSLATED INTO ENGLISH
MEANS HOUSE OF THE PEOPLE.

01:05:13.230 --> 01:05:15.960
AND IN CELTIC SPIRITUALITY,
THAT'S WHAT WE BELIEVE--

01:05:15.960 --> 01:05:17.730
THAT GOD DOESN'T NEED A HOUSE.

01:05:17.730 --> 01:05:20.530
GOD IS EVERYWHERE. HE'S
IN THE AIR WE BREATHE.

01:05:20.530 --> 01:05:22.330
IT'S LIKE THE PRAYER
OF ST. PATRICK.

01:05:22.330 --> 01:05:24.630
YOU KNOW, CHRIST BESIDE
ME, CHRIST ABOVE ME,

01:05:24.630 --> 01:05:27.360
CHRIST BELOW ME,
CHRIST AROUND ME.

01:05:27.360 --> 01:05:30.530
IF CHRIST IS YOUR
SAVIOR AND YOUR REDEEMER

01:05:30.530 --> 01:05:34.200
AND IF YOU CAN SEE CHRIST
IN EACH AND EVERY PERSON,

01:05:34.200 --> 01:05:42.100
THAT WOULD BE A
LOVELY WAY TO LIVE.

01:05:42.100 --> 01:05:44.660
Narrator: IN FEBRUARY 2007,

01:05:44.660 --> 01:05:47.600
8 MEN BROKE INTO
LERATONG HOSPICE,

01:05:47.600 --> 01:05:53.530
SHOT FATHER CREAGH TWICE,
AND LEFT HIM FOR DEAD.

01:05:53.530 --> 01:05:56.200
THE CALLOUS VIOLENCE
OF THE ROBBERS

01:05:56.200 --> 01:05:58.230
STUNNED HIM AND SHOOK HIS FAITH.

01:05:58.230 --> 01:06:01.330
BUT HE CHOSE NOT TO
SURRENDER TO HATRED.

01:06:01.330 --> 01:06:08.230
HE RETURNED TO LERATONG
AND CONTINUES HIS WORK.

01:06:08.230 --> 01:06:11.130
SOMETIMES YOU GET SO
ANGRY AT THE INJUSTICE,

01:06:11.130 --> 01:06:13.660
THAT YOU START BECOMING
WHAT YOU'RE FIGHTING.

01:06:13.660 --> 01:06:15.030
THAT'S WHEN YOU NEED YOUR FAITH.

01:06:15.030 --> 01:06:18.760
YOU'VE GOT TO HAVE SOMETHING
THAT'S DEEPER THAN YOUR ISSUE

01:06:18.760 --> 01:06:22.830
OR YOUR CAUSE OR YOUR
CAREER OR YOUR ENEMY

01:06:22.830 --> 01:06:24.660
THAT YOU COME BACK TO.

01:06:24.660 --> 01:06:29.560
[CHOIR SINGING]

01:06:29.560 --> 01:06:34.900
Armstrong: IN EVERY CASE,
RELIGION ISSUES A COMMAND--

01:06:34.900 --> 01:06:41.030
BE BETTER, BE MORE HUMANE,
BE MORE KIND, BE MORE JUST.

01:06:41.030 --> 01:06:45.260
RELIGIOUS TRUTH IS
A SUMMONS TO ACTION.

01:06:45.260 --> 01:06:50.500
AS THE BUDDHA PUT IT, ONCE A
MAN HAS ACHIEVED ENLIGHTENMENT,

01:06:50.500 --> 01:06:53.500
