FROM THE MOUNTAINTOP

01:06:53.500 --> 01:06:55.100
AND RETURN TO THE MARKETPLACE

01:06:55.100 --> 01:06:59.200
AND THERE PRACTICE COMPASSION
FOR ALL LIVING BEINGS.

01:06:59.200 --> 01:07:03.800
SO INHERENT IN
RELIGION AT ITS BEST

01:07:03.800 --> 01:07:46.400
IS A COMMITMENT TO
DOING GOOD IN THE WORLD.

01:07:46.400 --> 01:07:49.260
EACH HUMAN BEING HAS A SENSE

01:07:49.260 --> 01:07:51.260
THAT THERE ARE
THINGS THAT ARE RIGHT

01:07:51.260 --> 01:07:53.100
