THAT ARE WRONG.

01:07:53.100 --> 01:07:55.430
Rauf: WE ALL HAVE
A SENSE OF DECENCY,

01:07:55.430 --> 01:07:58.300
A SENSE OF JUSTICE,
A SENSE OF RIGHTNESS,

01:07:58.300 --> 01:07:59.960
OF HOW PEOPLE WANT
TO BE TREATED,

01:07:59.960 --> 01:08:02.460
OF THE HUMAN RIGHTS
AND THE HUMAN DIGNITY

01:08:02.460 --> 01:08:03.660
OF EVERY HUMAN BEING.

01:08:03.660 --> 01:08:06.030
THIS IS ALL THAT EVERYBODY
IN THE WORLD WANTS.

01:08:06.030 --> 01:08:08.300
Chopra: WHEN WE GO
BEYOND RACISM AND BIGOTRY

01:08:08.300 --> 01:08:12.100
AND HATRED AND PREJUDICE
AND NARROW NATIONALISM,

01:08:12.100 --> 01:08:14.400
THESE ARE THE WAYS
TO HEAL OURSELVES.

01:08:14.400 --> 01:08:17.930
Armstrong: THE CHALLENGE
TODAY IS FOR US TO IMPLEMENT

01:08:17.930 --> 01:08:22.260
THIS GLOBALLY SO WE
TREAT OTHER NATIONS

01:08:22.260 --> 01:08:24.830
AS WE WOULD WISH TO
BE TREATED OURSELVES.

01:08:24.830 --> 01:08:27.800
ALL OF HUMANITY NOW
IS BEING CHALLENGED

01:08:27.800 --> 01:08:30.160
TO TAKE A KIND OF
QUANTUM LEAP FORWARD

01:08:30.160 --> 01:08:31.400
INTO A NEW WAY OF THINKING.

01:08:31.400 --> 01:08:34.460
AND FROM THAT OTHER
WAY OF THINKING

01:08:34.460 --> 01:08:38.000
AND THE IMPERATIVE, THE MORAL
